FBIS4-59999 "drnes097_j_94026" FBIS-NES-94-097 Daily Report 19 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Salih Phones King Husayn, Discusses Crisis Salih Phones King Husayn, Discusses Crisis JN1905043894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 0330 GMT 19 May 94 JN1905043894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Presidential Council Chairman Brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih last night telephoned his brother His Majesty King Husayn Bin-Talal, king of the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan, and briefed him on the current situation in our country in light of the victories that our valiant Armed Forces, the forces of unity and legitimacy are scoring in repulsing the forces of rebellion and secession that have ignited the war in the homeland to implement their secessionist scheme of fragmenting the homeland. The two sides also discussed issues of mutual interest. The brother chairman valued the pan-Arab and noble stand of the brothers in Jordan, with his Majesty King Husayn at their head in support for our people and for unity and democracy in our country.
